{"tid":2050070,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國銀行體系嘅Fractional Reserve有冇可能已經成為歷史?","createTime":"2020-06-04T01:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T05:11:59.000Z","uid":351009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fbaebf0dd8e6ed3d5a63fa3d50efa2c5b7e86409","tid":2050070,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:30:48.000Z","msg":"根據聯儲局3月中公佈嘅政策，美國所有存款機構(Depository Institution)全部類型嘅法定存款準備金率(reserve requirement ratios, RRR)喺3月底已經降到零<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TsdJpR1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTsdJpR1.png&h=ed83419d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔記得咩係RRR嘅可以睇返呢幅圖<br />\n假如銀行收到$100存款而RRR係5%，銀行最多可以動用$95<br />\n而如果借晒$95出去，又收返所有做存款，銀行可以再動用$90.25...如此類推<br />\n借到最盡最多可以用呢$100創造$2000，造成貨幣擴張效應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/koWOA2W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkoWOA2W.png&h=e14a27d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRRR變零最直接嘅結果係銀行體系理論上唔駛留任何儲備<br />\n<strong>理論上</strong>可以借任何金額俾任何人，debt同leverage一定會增加<br />\n<br />\n08年之後好多人都覺得利息會正常化，但事實係低利息環境維持咗8年，遇到經濟問題又再減過 (2019年中已經開始減息，到pandemic先降到零)<br />\n聯儲局Q&amp;A有個問題係：係咪永久取消RRR?<br />\n答： 暫時無計劃重推RRR，日後會按情況調整RRR<br />\n<br />\n所以RRR有冇可能變成利息咁長期接近零? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擠提喺digital age係咪冇可能出現?<br />\n<br />\nExtra:<br />\n中國2020年1月份RRR係10%，今年減咗3次而家大約係8.4%<br />\n歐盟上次調整係2012年由2%減到1%，今次疫情無變<br />\n<br />\n美國原有嘅RRR<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QF4AfYM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQF4AfYM.png&h=3f364729&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ca3ea20e9057aa5af508e161946efade1eb5260","tid":2050070,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T01:34:23.000Z","msg":"咁都得...資產價格咪升到失控...?"},{"pid":"e59b41